author: Reuters Editorial
title: American stay-at-home order needed to prevent coronavirus spread: Fauci
description: Americans need to press on with efforts to contain the spread of coronavirus to start seeing the rates of infection come down, a top U.S. health official said on Monday after President Donald Trump extended a stay-at-home order through April.
